-- Hewlett-Packard names new head of services unit
-- 
-- Wed Nov 8, 2006 8:22am EST
-- http://www.reuters.com/article/2006/11/08/us-hewlettpackard-mccain-idUSWEN937720061108

 

 NEW YORK  (Reuters) - Personal computer maker Hewlett-Packard Co. ( HPQ.N ) on Wednesday named company executive John McCain to run its $15.5 billion global services business. 

 McCain, 47, has served as senior vice president of HP's consulting division since December 2005.